name: CSS Splitter Maven Plugin
tagline: Splits CSS stylesheets to smaller files
body:
# About
The CSS Splitter Maven Plugin is used to split the [CSS](http://www.w3.org/Style/CSS/) stylesheets to smaller files (parts) which contains maximum X rules.

# Versions
* [LATEST](/latest) - the latest version under development
